code: @Override protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     AtomixSetConfiguration configuration = this.configuration.copy().     // Bind options to the configuration object     setConfigurationProperties(configuration, parameters).     AtomixSetEndpoint endpoint = new AtomixSetEndpoint(uri, this, remaining).     endpoint.setConfiguration(configuration).     setProperties(endpoint, parameters).     return endpoint. }
// ********************************************** // Properties // ********************************************** public AtomixSetConfiguration getConfiguration() {     return this.configuration. }
/**  * The shared component configuration  */ public void setConfiguration(AtomixSetConfiguration configuration) {     this.configuration = configuration. }
